                    Your home away from home, set on the majestic waters of the Atlantic Ocean.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>


        <div class="rows">
            <div class="col text-center">
                <a id="check-availability-ro" href="#!" type="button" class="btn btn-success">Check Availability</a>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
